        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/135023831/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u135023831-3.jpg" alt="William" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36373646/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36373646/" class="">行为经济学和心理学的理论</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/135023831/" class=" " title="William">William</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="36373646">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36373646/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p36373646-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class=""> 
行为经济学和心理学的理论。对于有贫穷、紧张、快节奏、孤独等方面有深入分析；在工商管理实践中提出的具体分析有利于启发性思维。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-10-18 19:15</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">3人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p36373646-1.jpg" alt="读书笔记思维导图"><br><span class="pic-title">读书笔记思维导图</span></div>
行为经济学和心理学的理论。对于有贫穷、紧张、快节奏、孤独等方面有深入分析；在工商管理实践中提出的具体分析有利于启发性思维。
