          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35907524/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35907524/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/KimmyLovesIan/" class=" " title="ChuJewelry">ChuJewelry</a>
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="35907524">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">书围绕几个概念，讲稀缺带来的影响：
稀缺、管窥、带宽、余闲，重点讲解为什么稀缺会带来贫穷和忙碌，没有对如何调整做出明确说明。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35907524/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-08-17 15:05</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                书围绕几个概念，讲稀缺带来的影响：<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>稀缺、管窥、带宽、余闲，重点讲解为什么稀缺会带来贫穷和忙碌，没有对如何调整做出明确说明。
